videos.description: When Oregon State's Derrick Bruce goes into the lane, someone should have told him not to mess with Oregon's Chris Boucher, who swats his shot into the crowd.
videos.headline: Nation's leading shot blocker adds another... to the front row

videos.description: Oregon's Elgin Cook goes for the two-handed slam that hits the back rim, bounces straight up in the air and then swishes straight through the hoop for the oddest two-points ever.
videos.headline: Cook scores the weirdest slam dunk in history
